=begin pod

=head1 Requirements for CSV::Editor

(Imported from user's Requirements.txt)

=item Header line with field names; separators are one of: C<|>, C<,>, C<;>.
=item Field names are ASCII letters, digits, or hyphen; unique.
=item Records may have empty fields; trailing empties may omit separators.
=item Whitespace padding around separators is insignificant.
=item Lines starting with C<#> are ignored except for file save.
=item A record starting with C<=finish> ends effective content.
=item GUI launched as C<csv-edit $file> with Save, Exit, FitWidth.
=item Scrolling both directions; resizable widget window.

=end pod
